Description: This offering is for a really nice Ibanez RG Iron Label RGIR20FE electric guitar and Ibanez hardshell case that are in nice condition. I got this guitar as partial trade for another guitar. I'm trying to downsize, so it's for sale. These guitars are of nice build quality and components. The color is snow white. I can't see where there is any fret wear at all. It has pretty heavy gauge strings on it and the EMG pickups in it sound about as good as it gets. The strings are fresh and the intonation has been set with a high dollar stroboscope. It has been meticulously cleaned, polished and has a premium setup for standard tuning. The fret ends have been dressed to silky smooth. It only has a few pinhead small dings, some really light wispy dusting scratching and a couple light scratches. Still in very nice condition. It will be packed up with lots of love and care for a safe shipment. Very nice guitar that I’m sure the new owner of this guitar will be very pleased to have. All questions are welcome. Please check out my other listings. The guitar can be purchased without the hardshell case. I'll refund $50 of your payment if you would rather not have the nice case. :)NOTE: It's also listed on Reverb. If it sells there first, this listing is void.Buyer to pay $47 for shipping and a very well packed fully insured shipment to any lower 48 state. I’ll be listing more guitars, amps and guitar gear so please check out my other auctions often. Please take a minute and check way back through my feedback record here and on Reverb to know that you can buy completely comfortably here. It’s been a while, but I’ve successfully sold a LOT of high end guitars and gear on here since March of 2000. Thanks very much! :)
Title: NICE Ibanez RG Iron Label RGIR20FE Guitar & Hardshell Case, Snow White
